# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:41
translate spanish hwb_s12b_a974ec70:

    # "For having been mostly asleep, and in the dark, it looks like I did an okay job parking."
    "Para haber estado casi dormida, y en la oscuridad, parece que hice un trabajo decente estacionando."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:43
translate spanish hwb_s12b_7e108dfa:

    # "By which I mean that we’re actually in one of the designated camping spaces."
    "Con lo que quiero decir que en realidad estamos en uno de los espacios designados para acampar."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:45
translate spanish hwb_s12b_49675620:

    # "That's more than I can say for a lot of the others here."
    "Eso es más de lo que puedo decir de muchos otros aquí."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s12b_92a2161b:

    # "Tents cover nearly every patch of land that doesn’t have an RV on it. Some even come right up against the road itself, causing the few cars that pass by to have to hug the edge."
    "Las tiendas cubren casi cada pedazo de tierra que no tiene una casa rodante. Algunas incluso llegan hasta la carretera, obligando a los pocos autos que pasan a pegarse al borde."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:51
translate spanish hwb_s12b_1d6ab6b3:

    # "Just like back in Shiprock, this is a fiasco."
    "Igual que en Shiprock, esto es un desastre."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:53
translate spanish hwb_s12b_6be34ada:

    # "Squads of little kids rampage around, squirting each other (and everyone else) with water guns and just being in the way."
    "Escuadrones de niños pequeños corretean, rociándose entre sí (y a todos los demás) con pistolas de agua y estorbando."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:58
translate spanish hwb_s12b_4c3f2157:

    # "One little brat runs up to us and holds up his squirt gun like he’s going to shoot me. But the death glare that I give sends him running back in the other direction."
    "Un pequeño mocoso se acerca a nosotros y levanta su pistola de agua como si fuera a dispararme. Pero la mirada asesina que le doy lo hace salir corriendo en la otra dirección."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:63
translate spanish hwb_s12b_21519014:

    # Marina "Not a fan of kids?"
    Marina "Не любишь детей?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:67
translate spanish hwb_s12b_c18a09b6:

    # Amber "Not the rotten ones."
    Amber "Таких - нет."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:71
translate spanish hwb_s12b_301cd6ab:

    # "Marina, on the other hand, waves at the retreating boy, and giggles as a weak burst of water hits her."
    "Marina, por otro lado, le saluda al niño que se aleja, y se ríe cuando un débil chorro de agua la alcanza."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:75
translate spanish hwb_s12b_bbb6e04a:

    # Amber "I dunno how you can stand it."
    Amber "Понятия не имею, как ты это терпишь."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:79
translate spanish hwb_s12b_46432871:

    # Marina "They’re just kids!"
    Marina "Они же просто дети!"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:83
translate spanish hwb_s12b_85fb3303:

    # Marina "Besides, I’m pretty used to it."
    Marina "К тому же, я к такому привыкла."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:87
translate spanish hwb_s12b_cf758769:

    # Amber "Big family, right?"
    Amber "Большая семья?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:91
translate spanish hwb_s12b_aaa9bcf8:

    # Marina "Yep!"
    Marina "Ага!"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:93
translate spanish hwb_s12b_a3f6b3c9:

    # "We start to walk in the direction of the canyon itself, pausing sometimes to let cars or tour groups pass us by."
    "Empezamos a caminar hacia el cañón, deteniéndonos a veces para dejar pasar autos o grupos de turistas."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:95
translate spanish hwb_s12b_90b7fa3c:

    # Amber "This is such a mess. Wonder how many of them are treasure hunters."
    Amber "Что за суматоха. Интересно кто из них ищет сокровище."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:99
translate spanish hwb_s12b_53f24fd4:

    # Marina "Well it’s the Grand Canyon, so a lot of people are probably just regular tourists, right?"
    Marina "Ну, это ведь Гранд каньон, так что большинство людей здесь обычные туристы, верно?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:101
translate spanish hwb_s12b_ced53931:

    # Amber "Yeah, probably."
    Amber "Да, скорее всего."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:103
translate spanish hwb_s12b_882aa119:

    # Amber "I feel bad for them. And all the other people who just wanna enjoy these parks."
    Amber "Немного их жалко. И всех остальных людей, которые пришли сюда просто насладиться природой."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:107
translate spanish hwb_s12b_6bcfff12:

    # Marina "You really hate people, huh?"
    Marina "Недолюбливаешь людей?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:109
translate spanish hwb_s12b_09553a7f:

    # Amber "What? Where’d that come from?"
    Amber "Что? С чего ты вообще взяла?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:113
translate spanish hwb_s12b_de7269d1:

    # Marina "I dunno, you’re just always complaining about there being too many people around."
    Marina "Не знаю, просто ты все время бурчишь про то, как много людей вокруг."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:115
translate spanish hwb_s12b_d954c11b:

    # "Do I really complain that much?"
    "¿De verdad me quejo tanto?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:119
translate spanish hwb_s12b_6736ed66:

    # "Thinking about it, I guess I do."
    "Pensándolo bien, supongo que sí."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:123
translate spanish hwb_s12b_73679322:

    # Amber "I don’t hate people. I just don’t like when it’s all chaotic like this."
    Amber "Я не ненавижу людей, просто не люблю такую суматоху и хаос."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:127
translate spanish hwb_s12b_7f177fcc:

    # Marina "So you don't like crowds, then?"
    Marina "Значит ты не любишь находиться в толпе?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:129
translate spanish hwb_s12b_c5594a6c:

    # Amber "That’s closer, yeah."
    Amber "Вот это уже больше похоже на правду."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:131
translate spanish hwb_s12b_1896a3f1:

    # Marina "Kinda weird that you’re so hyped for this music thing then, don't you think? Isn’t that gonna be the biggest crowd yet?"
    Marina "Тогда довольно странно, что ты так ждешь этот концерт, не думаешь? Разве там не будет еще больше народу?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:135
translate spanish hwb_s12b_9196aa55:

    # Amber "Sure, but that’s different."
    Amber "Ну да, но это другое дело."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:139
translate spanish hwb_s12b_cbb21f84:

    # Marina "Why?"
    Marina "Почему?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:143
translate spanish hwb_s12b_9cc534bc:

    # Amber "I dunno, just is."
    Amber "Я не знаю, просто."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:145
translate spanish hwb_s12b_cbb21f84_1:

    # Marina "Why?"
    Marina "Почему?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:149
translate spanish hwb_s12b_beec74ac:

    # Amber "What are you, five? No wonder you get along with kids so well."
    Amber "Тебе что, пять лет? Неудивительно, что ты так комфортно чувствуешь себя с детьми."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:155
translate spanish hwb_s12b_21eb7dd4:

    # "We both laugh."
    "Ambas nos reímos."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:159
translate spanish hwb_s12b_cc948247:

    # Amber "But… I guess it’s just because everyone is there for the same thing. You have something in common with them."
    Amber "Но... все-таки, мне кажется, это все потому, что на концерте все пришли ради одного. Так что у тебя есть что-то общее с этой толпой."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:163
translate spanish hwb_s12b_e1cb01b1:

    # Marina "Isn’t everyone here for the same thing?"
    Marina "А здесь разве люди собрались не ради одного?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:167
translate spanish hwb_s12b_b610ac08:

    # Amber "Yeah, but…"
    Amber "Да, но..."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:173
translate spanish hwb_s12b_c2c35b83:

    # "I struggle to find an explanation."
    "Lucho por encontrar una explicación."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:177
translate spanish hwb_s12b_826e45b4:

    # "But she laughs it off and shrugs."
    "Pero ella lo toma con risa y se encoge de hombros."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:183
translate spanish hwb_s12b_14b83302:

    # Marina "I’m just kidding anyway. You can’t be the only who teases."
    Marina "Да ладно, я просто шучу. Не только же тебе издеваться надо мной."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:185
translate spanish hwb_s12b_1ab4bf0b:

    # Marina "You don’t like big crowds, and that’s fine!"
    Marina "Ты не любишь толпу, ну и что с того!"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:191
translate spanish hwb_s12b_9d851916:

    # Amber "What about you?"
    Amber "А что насчет тебя?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:197
translate spanish hwb_s12b_66a5c89c:

    # Marina "I think it’s fun! And besides, you get to meet all sorts of cool people."
    Marina "А мне нравится! К тому же так можно встретить много разных людей."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:201
translate spanish hwb_s12b_8aa74292:

    # Marina "Who knows, maybe you’ll meet a special someone or a long-lost relative or something."
    Marina "Кто знает, может ты встретишь кого-нибудь особенного или типа того."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:205
translate spanish hwb_s12b_b9a109c9:

    # "\"Special someone,\" huh?"
    "\"Alguien especial\", ¿eh?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:209
translate spanish hwb_s12b_3b1da29e:

    # Amber "Maybe. Would be pretty unlikely though."
    Amber "Может быть. Хотя это маловероятно."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:211
translate spanish hwb_s12b_d29229b4:

    # Marina "Probably. But it’s still fun to think about."
    Marina "Наверное. Но это все равно забавно."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:215
translate spanish hwb_s12b_0755cd76:

    # Marina "And speaking of odds…"
    Marina "Говоря о маловероятности..."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:217
translate spanish hwb_s12b_828df7c1:

    # Marina "Amber…"
    Marina "Эмбер…"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:219
translate spanish hwb_s12b_ff446093:

    # "Marina points at another cluster of motorhomes down the road."
    "Marina señala otro grupo de casas rodantes calle abajo."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:221
translate spanish hwb_s12b_1ff58c45:

    # "I follow her gaze, immediately understanding."
    "Sigo su mirada, entendiendo de inmediato."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:223
translate spanish hwb_s12b_2b57ba61:

    # "Taking up two spaces, because of size and bad parking, is a familiar titan of an RV."
    "Ocupando dos espacios, por su tamaño y mal estacionamiento, está un titán familiar de casa rodante."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:227
translate spanish hwb_s12b_e4dce664:

    # Amber "God, no."
    Amber "Боже, только не это."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:234
translate spanish hwb_s12b_1c1a1000:

    # "But Marina’s already heading towards it."
    "Pero Marina ya se dirige hacia ella."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:236
translate spanish hwb_s12b_f15e338c:

    # "My nemesis."
    "Mi némesis."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:238
translate spanish hwb_s12b_338a8057:

    # "Mariah’s motorhome."
    "La casa rodante de Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:248
translate spanish hwb_s12b_a3da3395:

    # "The door flies open, seconds before Marina reaches it."
    "La puerta se abre de golpe, segundos antes de que Marina llegue."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:263
translate spanish hwb_s12b_ba65dd45:

    # "Out strolls Joseph, Tess close behind."
    "Sale Joseph, con Tess justo detrás."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:265
translate spanish hwb_s12b_5bb694ec:

    # Joseph "You call that a break? You’ve had boyfriends that last longer."
    Joseph "И ты это называешь перерывом? Да ты со своим парнем встречалась дольше."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:267
translate spanish hwb_s12b_983dbda4:

    # Tess "Sis has never had a boyfriend."
    Tess "У сестренки ведь не было парня."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:269
translate spanish hwb_s12b_b93ae3a4:

    # Joseph "My point exactly."
    Joseph "Ну а я о чем."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:271
translate spanish hwb_s12b_88eb0dcf:

    # Mariah "Quit your moaning. You two just need more work ether."
    Mariah "А ну хватит ныть. Кто не работает, тот не ест."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:273
translate spanish hwb_s12b_604d8481:

    # Joseph "You mean ‘ethics,’ but you’ve probably never heard the word."
    Joseph "Что-то по тебе этого не заметно."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:282
translate spanish hwb_s12b_51b6aec8:

    # "Mariah appears in the doorway, leaning on a shovel. I can see her about to retort, but then she spots either me or Marina, and her glare is replaced with a smug grin."
    "Mariah aparece en la entrada, apoyada en una pala. Veo que está a punto de responder, pero entonces me ve a mí o a Marina, y su mirada se reemplaza por una sonrisa burlona."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:287
translate spanish hwb_s12b_1562b29b:

    # Mariah "Well, well, well. Look who finally caught up."
    Mariah "Ну надо же, посмотрите-ка, кто в конце концов объявился."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:291
translate spanish hwb_s12b_06ee627a:

    # Marina "Hey guys!"
    Marina "Привет, народ!"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:293
translate spanish hwb_s12b_8cb64224:

    # Joseph "Oh, hey there, ladies."
    Joseph "О, привет, дамы."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:298
translate spanish hwb_s12b_14c16b62:

    # "I sigh and speed up my glacial pace. May as well get this over with."
    "Suspiro y acelero mi paso glacial. Mejor terminar con esto de una vez."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:300
translate spanish hwb_s12b_8235ffc3:

    # "Mariah picks up a crate of tools from beside her and carries them out, before shoving the crate into Joseph’s hands."
    "Mariah levanta una caja de herramientas que está a su lado y la saca, antes de meterla en las manos de Joseph."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:302
translate spanish hwb_s12b_6a3aa7a3:

    # "His knees buckle at the weight, and he sets it on the ground."
    "Sus rodillas se doblan por el peso, y la coloca en el suelo."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:304
translate spanish hwb_s12b_b4d1ef82:

    # Mariah "Did you follow our dust all the way here?"
    Mariah "Шли по нашим следам прямиком до сюда?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:308
translate spanish hwb_s12b_b7fd650a:

    # Amber "I wish we’d seen it, so we could’ve stayed away."
    Amber "Если бы мы и смотрели на ваши следы, то только для того, чтобы держаться подальше."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:310
translate spanish hwb_s12b_e2ef75c2:

    # Mariah "Maybe you should go now and get a head start on the next piece, before we find the one here."
    Mariah "Может вам лучше уехать, чтобы получить фору в поисках следующей части сокровища, а мы пока найдем ту, которая находится здесь."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:312
translate spanish hwb_s12b_fd41e796:

    # "She clutches her shovel like a sword and points it at me."
    "Aprieta su pala como si fuera una espada y la apunta hacia mí."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:316
translate spanish hwb_s12b_459273d4:

    # Mariah "Unless you’re gonna fight us on this one too."
    Mariah "Если только вы не собираетесь и здесь с нами потягаться."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:318
translate spanish hwb_s12b_33f521d6:

    # "I raise my hands in surrender."
    "Levanto las manos en señal de rendición."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:320
translate spanish hwb_s12b_b1805c21:

    # Amber "We already had one bust at Canyon de Chelly. This one’s all yours to screw up."
    Amber "Мы уже попытали удачу в Каньоне-де-Шей. Теперь ваша очередь ощущать вкус провала."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:322
translate spanish hwb_s12b_b67515db:

    # "The shovel drops a couple inches, either as a response or because her arm’s getting sore."
    "La pala baja un par de centímetros, ya sea como respuesta o porque su brazo se está cansando."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:326
translate spanish hwb_s12b_93103343:

    # Mariah "'Canyon de Chelly?' But there's only one Grand Canyon!"
    Mariah "“Каньон-де-Шейи”? Но есть всего один Гранд Каньон!"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:330
translate spanish hwb_s12b_1b187854:

    # Joseph "There's more than one canyon in the world, Mare."
    Joseph "В мире полным-полно каньонов, Мария."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:332
translate spanish hwb_s12b_5f911c9e:

    # Amber "Figured it was there at the Mummy Cave Ruins, but we didn’t find anything."
    Amber "Мы выяснили, что часть должна быть в руинах «Пещеры Мумий», но мы ничего не нашли."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:334
translate spanish hwb_s12b_f21b6655:

    # Amber "So if you wanna search all 2,000 miles of the Grand Canyon then good luck."
    Amber "Так что если уж вам хочется обыскать все 3000 километров Гранд каньона, дерзайте."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:338
translate spanish hwb_s12b_624bf04f:

    # Mariah "Dammit!" with hpunch
    Mariah "Черт побери!" with hpunch

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:342
translate spanish hwb_s12b_5722e9a1:

    # "Mariah throws down her hands and the tool-bag slips from her, plummeting onto Joseph’s foot. Hard. The crates in his hand are the next to fall, this time on to the other foot."
    "Mariah baja las manos y la bolsa de herramientas se le resbala, cayendo sobre el pie de Joseph. Con fuerza. Las cajas que tiene en la mano son las siguientes en caer, esta vez sobre el otro pie."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:344
translate spanish hwb_s12b_c9837085:

    # "The boxes burst open, flooding the ground with heavy hammers and wrenches."
    "Las cajas se abren de golpe, inundando el suelo con martillos y llaves pesadas."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:346
translate spanish hwb_s12b_15e8de33:

    # "A gasp escapes his mouth, then silence."
    "Un jadeo escapa de su boca, luego silencio."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:350
translate spanish hwb_s12b_4c0afafc:

    # Tess "Are you gonna get drunk and cry yourself to sleep again, Sis?"
    Tess "Опять напьешься и будешь рыдать, пока не заснешь, сестренка?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:352
translate spanish hwb_s12b_5bab2952:

    # "Somehow, through pained grunts, Joseph manages to speak."
    "De alguna manera, entre gruñidos de dolor, Joseph logra hablar."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:356
translate spanish hwb_s12b_71aeddb9:

    # Joseph "The limit is once per week."
    Joseph "Она таким занимается не чаще раза в неделю."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:360
translate spanish hwb_s12b_1e26c6f7:

    # "Mariah's eyes twitch."
    "Los ojos de Mariah se contraen."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:362
translate spanish hwb_s12b_229858f9:

    # "In one smooth motion, she whirls around and clonks her companions's heads, huffs, and crosses her arms."
    "En un movimiento fluido, gira y golpea las cabezas de sus compañeros, resopla y cruza los brazos."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:368
translate spanish hwb_s12b_76d2a576:

    # "Joseph reacts like any normal human being and rubs his head to soothe his neverending pain. Tess hardly acknowledges it, wobbling back and forth like a human bobblehead."
    "Joseph reacciona como cualquier ser humano normal y se frota la cabeza para aliviar su dolor interminable. Tess apenas lo nota, balanceándose de un lado a otro como un muñeco de resorte humano."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:370
translate spanish hwb_s12b_153e38f6:

    # "I don't think I'll ever get over how creepy that girl is."
    "Creo que nunca me acostumbraré a lo espeluznante que es esa chica."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:375
translate spanish hwb_s12b_91d556f3:

    # "She clonks Joseph again for good measure. Marina and I both wince."
    "Golpea a Joseph otra vez por si acaso. Marina y yo nos estremecemos."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:377
translate spanish hwb_s12b_3da0b10f:

    # "I imagine this is how it was for Howard when he first met Linda."
    "Imagino que así fue cuando Howard conoció a Linda."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:384
translate spanish hwb_s12b_862b7c90:

    # Tess "At least we’d get to see the canyon that way."
    Tess "Ну хотя бы мы сможем увидеть каньон."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:389
translate spanish hwb_s12b_936ec602:

    # Amber "Jesus!"
    Amber "Боже!"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:391
translate spanish hwb_s12b_4872ad2a:

    # "From out of nowhere, Tess pops up at my side."
    "De la nada, Tess aparece a mi lado."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:395
translate spanish hwb_s12b_40467cb6:

    # Joseph "Tess has been wanting to go out and see the sights, but Mariah’s too busy breaking her back for that."
    Joseph "Тесс хотела прогуляться и насладиться видами, но как видите, Мария слишком занята."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:399
translate spanish hwb_s12b_563f3478:

    # Marina "Big sisters are bossy, huh?"
    Marina "Старшие сестры такие вредные, верно?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:412
translate spanish hwb_s12b_a803e864:

    # "Tess nods, which prompts Marina to stoop down and hug her apathetic kindred spirit."
    "Tess asiente, lo que hace que Marina se agache y abrace a su apático espíritu afín."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:414
translate spanish hwb_s12b_04ec1008:

    # Marina "You’re not alone!"
    Marina "Ты не одинока!"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:416
translate spanish hwb_s12b_a6ae3704:

    # "Marina looks up at me, eyes big."
    "Marina me mira, con los ojos muy abiertos."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:420
translate spanish hwb_s12b_67967d47:

    # Marina "Can we keep her? She's so cute!"
    Marina "Давай возьмем ее с собой, она такая милая!"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:424
translate spanish hwb_s12b_4760100c:

    # Mariah "That’s property theft!"
    Mariah "Это называется кража собственности!"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:428
translate spanish hwb_s12b_81e08e85:

    # Amber "Sorry, only one stray at a time."
    Amber "Прости, но мне лишняя обуза ни к чему."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:430
translate spanish hwb_s12b_2ceccb76:

    # Marina "Aww."
    Marina "Жаль..."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s12b_bc78c801:

    # "Marina releases Tess and reaches out her hand as they float apart."
    "Marina suelta a Tess y extiende la mano mientras se separan flotando."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:442
translate spanish hwb_s12b_e7303985:

    # Amber "Anyway, let’s get going. If they’re gonna waste all day here we can at least leave them to it."
    Amber "Ну да ладно, пора выдвигаться. Раз они тратят время в пустую, нечего нам брать с них пример."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:444
translate spanish hwb_s12b_6c447508:

    # "But Mariah waves her shovel in Joseph’s face."
    "Pero Mariah agita su pala frente a la cara de Joseph."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:448
translate spanish hwb_s12b_0241322e:

    # Mariah "Pick up our crap. We’re gonna rethink our strategy."
    Mariah "Подбери эту хрень. Нам нужно обдумать, как мы будем действовать."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:452
translate spanish hwb_s12b_a116ad57:

    # Joseph "'Crap?'"
    Joseph "“Хрень”?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:454
translate spanish hwb_s12b_86384231:

    # Mariah "Yes, this crap."
    Mariah "Да, вот эту хрень."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:456
translate spanish hwb_s12b_f99c8901:

    # "She taps the crate that she forced on him just minutes ago."
    "Golpea la caja que le obligó a cargar hace apenas unos minutos."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:462
translate spanish hwb_s12b_1e802ffe:

    # "Joseph covers Tess’ ears then mutters something that I can’t make out"
    "Joseph cubre los oídos de Tess y luego murmura algo que no logro entender."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:466
translate spanish hwb_s12b_23d7ffac:

    # Marina "Wait, I have an idea!"
    Marina "Стойте, у меня есть идея!"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:474
translate spanish hwb_s12b_af3a47d9:

    # "Four pairs of eyes turn to look at her."
    "Cuatro pares de ojos se giran para mirarla."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:478
translate spanish hwb_s12b_7aa721fc:

    # Marina "Me and Amber were about to go sightseeing. Why don’t you guys come with us?"
    Marina "Мы с Эмбер собираемся осмотреть окрестности. Почему бы вам не присоединиться к нам?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:484
translate spanish hwb_s12b_37c58d76:

    # "{color=#ee320f}Amber{/color} & {color=#ffdab3}Mariah{/color}" "That's a terrible idea."
    MariahAmber "Ужасная идея."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:490
translate spanish hwb_s12b_63eff13e:

    # Amber "Hey, we agree on something."
    Amber "Эй, мы же кое о чем договаривались."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:494
translate spanish hwb_s12b_a084605e:

    # "But Tess’ eyes sparkle with determination, nodding as she reaches up to tug on Mariah's suit."
    "Pero los ojos de Tess brillan con determinación, asintiendo mientras se estira para tirar del traje de Mariah."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:496
translate spanish hwb_s12b_56428dc7:

    # Marina "That’s one vote yes!"
    Marina "Это один голос за!"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:500
translate spanish hwb_s12b_3d908320:

    # "She turns to me, pleading look in her eyes, hoping to make it two yes votes."
    "Se vuelve hacia mí, con una mirada suplicante en sus ojos, esperando conseguir un segundo voto a favor."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:506
translate spanish hwb_s12b_03388f9d:

    # Joseph "I think that sounds like a good time, too."
    Joseph "Ну а что, неплохая идея, как по мне."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:510
translate spanish hwb_s12b_f3de10aa:

    # Joseph "It’d be a nice {i}break{/i}."
    Joseph "Звучит как {i}перерыв{/i}."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:514
translate spanish hwb_s12b_749b3c83:

    # Mariah "I forbid it! You’ve already had a break!"
    Mariah "Я запрещаю! У вас уже был один перерыв!"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:516
translate spanish hwb_s12b_79a47d8f:

    # Mariah "We have too much to focus on. Getting distracted by dusty, old rocks is the last thing we need."
    Mariah "У нас предостаточно дел. Нечего отвлекаться на старые, пыльные камни."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:518
translate spanish hwb_s12b_48e7c1db:

    # Joseph "You always say that, but look at her!"
    Joseph "Ты так всегда говоришь, но вот глянь на нее!"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:520
translate spanish hwb_s12b_30b21d6a:

    # "He points to Tess, her face shining with interest since the word ‘sightseeing.’"
    "Señala a Tess, cuyo rostro se ilumina de interés desde que escuchó la palabra 'turismo'."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:522
translate spanish hwb_s12b_ccfb735b:

    # Joseph "When did she last show interest in something? Hell, has she {i}ever{/i} shown interest in something?"
    Joseph "Когда она в последний раз была так в чем-нибудь заинтересована? Черт возьми, она {i}вообще{/i} была в чем-то заинтересована в последнее время?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:526
translate spanish hwb_s12b_e71d3d0e:

    # Mariah "We're still not going."
    Mariah "Мы все равно никуда не пойдем."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:530
translate spanish hwb_s12b_d916094f:

    # "An irritable groan rumbles through Joseph's throat, but he still looks as casual and relaxed as he usually does."
    "Un gruñido irritable retumba en la garganta de Joseph, pero aún así se ve tan casual y relajado como siempre."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:532
translate spanish hwb_s12b_d124f28c:

    # Joseph "Look, we're not always going to do what you want just because you say so."
    Joseph "Слушай, мы не будем все время делать то, что ты хочешь только потому, что ты так сказала."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:536
translate spanish hwb_s12b_8108d586:

    # Joseph "We're going, and if we have to, we'll force you to come along."
    Joseph "Мы все равно пойдем, а если придется, то и тебя заставим."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:542
translate spanish hwb_s12b_dbae7b6a:

    # "Marina laughs awkwardly."
    "Marina se ríe con incomodidad."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:544
translate spanish hwb_s12b_6a8edb59:

    # Marina "It's fine, it's fine. You guys don't have to come if you don't want to."
    Marina "Все в порядке, если не хотите, мы пойдем вдвоем."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:562
translate spanish hwb_s12b_1a043821:

    # "But it's too late for that. Mariah lets out a single, disingenuous 'ha,' and marches to Joseph."
    "Pero ya es demasiado tarde para eso. Mariah suelta un único 'ja' fingido y marcha hacia Joseph."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:566
translate spanish hwb_s12b_7dd38b7c:

    # Mariah "You’re gonna force me to go, huh?"
    Mariah "Заставишь меня, говоришь?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:570
translate spanish hwb_s12b_99857935:

    # Joseph "That’s right."
    Joseph "Именно."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:572
translate spanish hwb_s12b_ec80eb9e:

    # "She stares him down—or up, to be accurate. The top of her head only reaches up to his chin. Regardless, she gives him a nasty grin and repeatedly pokes his chest for daring to defy her."
    "Lo mira fijamente—o hacia arriba, para ser precisos. La parte superior de su cabeza apenas llega a su barbilla. Aun así, le dedica una sonrisa malvada y le pica el pecho repetidamente por atreverse a desafiarla."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:574
translate spanish hwb_s12b_94be4d76:

    # "This doesn't seem to phase him, though, as his lips curl into an ominous smile."
    "Sin embargo, esto no parece afectarlo, ya que sus labios se curvan en una sonrisa siniestra."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:576
translate spanish hwb_s12b_5cf25309:

    # Mariah "And how exactly do you plan to do that?"
    Mariah "Ну и как ты собираешься это сделать?"

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:462
translate spanish hwb_s12b_6bbaf854:

    # "Joseph covers Tess’ ears then mutters something that I can’t make out."
    "Joseph tapa los oídos de Tess y luego murmura algo que no logro distinguir."

# game/script/hwb_s12b.rpy:183
translate spanish hwb_s12b_7c60074a:

    # Marina "I’m just kidding anyway. You can’t be the only one who teases."
    Marina "Да ладно, я просто шучу. Не только же тебе издеваться надо мной."

